OL,3,CFree sea safety sessions for Channel
OL,4,CIsland youngsters
OL,6,FIn Jersey, the scheme is being run by
OL,7,FJersey Sport and the Bosdet Foundation.
OL,9,FYear 5 pupils from St Martins were
OL,10,Frecently at Rozel Beach to learn their
OL,11,Fsea safety skills
OL,13,FJersey Sport's Swimming Officer
OL,14,FMartine Le Guilcher explained: "Living
OL,15,Fon an island, we're surrounded by
OL,16,Fwater, so kids can access the sea all
OL,17,Fthe time.
