OL,3,CFree sea safety sessions for Channel
OL,4,CIsland youngsters
OL,6,F"But if it's not accessed properly, it
OL,7,Fcould be dangerous, so we want to give
OL,8,Fthem the skills and the knowledge to
OL,9,Fswim without having to worry."
OL,11,FGuernsey schoolchildren have been
OL,12,Ftaking their sea swimming lessons at
OL,13,FPembroke Bay.
OL,15,FGuernsey Sports Commission's Steve
OL,16,FSharman said: "It's an introduction
OL,17,Ffor these children to the wonderful
OL,18,Fenvironment that has to offer, which
OL,19,Fis the sea.
