OL,3,CFree sea safety sessions for Channel
OL,4,CIsland youngsters
OL,6,F"There are issues around
OL,7,Fintergenerational families where they
OL,8,Fhave never come to the beach.
OL,10,F"So It's important not only for the
OL,11,Fexperience to be out in the natural
OL,12,Fworld and understand the risk
OL,13,Fassessments."
OL,15,FLast month, Guernsey Sports Commission
OL,16,Fhelped to install a new swimming
OL,17,Fplatform at Pembroke to encourage
OL,18,Fsafer swimming practices.
OL,20,FSteve said it would "promote safe and
OL,21,Fenjoyable sea swimming for all ages".
